---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Return & Refund Policy — 8EyeTieDye"
  description="Return and refund policy for 8EyeTieDye print-on-demand products."
>
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-3xl">
    <h1
      class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold dye-gradient-text mb-8"
    >
      Return & Refund Policy
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg space-y-6 text-gray-300">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Effective Date: March 21, 2026</p>

      <p>
        Because every 8EyeTieDye product is custom-printed with a unique AI
        design, we cannot accept returns for change of mind. However, we stand
        behind the quality of our products and will make it right if something
        goes wrong.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Defective or Damaged Items
      </h2>
      <p>
        If your order arrives with a manufacturing defect, print error, or
        shipping damage, contact us within <strong>14 days</strong> of delivery. We'll
        offer a replacement or full refund at no additional cost to you.
      </p>
      <p>
        To file a claim, email us at
        <a
          href="mailto:support@8eyetiedye.com"
          class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300"
        >
          support@8eyetiedye.com
        </a>
        with:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Your order ID</li>
        <li>A photo of the defective/damaged item</li>
        <li>A brief description of the issue</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Wrong Size or Item
      </h2>
      <p>
        If you receive the wrong size or a different product than what you
        ordered, contact us within <strong>14 days</strong> and we'll send the correct
        item at no charge.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Cancellations
      </h2>
      <p>
        Orders cannot be cancelled once production has started. Because our
        products are custom-made, production typically begins within 24 hours of
        payment. If you need to cancel, contact us as soon as possible and we'll
        do our best to accommodate your request.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Refund Process
      </h2>
      <p>
        Approved refunds are processed to the original payment method within
        5–10 business days. You'll receive an email confirmation when your
        refund is issued.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Non-Refundable Items
      </h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Mystery packs (designs are delivered digitally upon purchase)</li>
        <li>Roll credits (consumed upon use)</li>
        <li>Items reported after the 14-day window</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Contact Us
      </h2>
      <p>
        For any questions about returns or refunds, email
        <a
          href="mailto:support@8eyetiedye.com"
          class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300"
        >
          support@8eyetiedye.com
        </a>
        with your order ID and we'll respond within 1–2 business days.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
